===Etymology===
A {{NL.}} word derived by Sir Humphry Davy in 1808, from {{etyl|la}} ''[[calx]]'' ("lime", "limestone") because it occurs in limestone.<ref>''Chambers Dictionary of Etymology'', Robert K. Barnhart (ed.), Chambers, 1988</ref>

